snippet.title: DC Daily Ep. 71: Exclusive interview with AQUAMAN stars Jason Momoa and Amber Heard
snippet.description:
For even more DC Daily, be sure to subscribe to DC Universe at https://yourdcu.com/ytdcd71
 
Today on DC Daily, we have an exclusive interview with AQUAMAN stars, Jason Momoa and Amber Heard. Our panel discusses their thoughts on the AQUAMAN movie (no spoilers), and they chat about this week’s AQUAMAN comic that features a brand new creative team. We also take a look at the new DC Universe DOOM PATROL trailer. Plus, Skylar Grey sings “Everything I Need” from the AQUAMAN movie, and we unwrap a super gift on set! 
 
DC Daily is a five-days-a-week webseries offering an unprecedented look inside the world of DC. Featuring a team of hosts and regular first looks and exclusives, each episode offers news, discussions, announcements, interviews and much more. Subscribe so you never miss an episode…or even better, sign up for DC Universe for extended episodes featuring exclusive panel discussions that you’ll only see there!
